{"tid":1826723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方就周日遊行發岀反對通知書理據","createTime":"2020-01-16T10:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T13:23:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1404fafede50d21f126a54ad969fb13a52a188","tid":1826723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">劉頴匡今日收到警方回覆，稱反對他擬於周日舉行的遊行。警方在書面回覆中表示，在去年12月8日及今年1月1日港島區遊行中，開始前、進行期間及結束後，警方在附近拘捕14人並檢獲刀具、鐵鎚等。警方亦接獲23宗嚴重破壞及縱火案件，及3宗持不同意見市民被打案件。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱由於近日社會氣氛，以及近來公眾集會遊行後發生的違法及暴力事件，警方有理由相信這次遊行的參與者，可能進行的行為不在劉頴匡控制範圍之內。警方亦有理由相信他沒有能力確保參與者及其他市民的人身安全。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93-%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%83%85%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%81%AE%E6%89%93%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E9%2581%25AE%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=5eb7954d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E9%2581%25AE%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=f15dea12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%B0%91%E9%96%